            "text": "Replier is always striving to get better and to that end she plays on the club circuit as well. I love competing in tournaments whether they're local level or national level and the club environment is just so fun and it is something I really love to do is just compete and every weekend you know we're traveling to different cities and spending a lot of time on the court.",
